  31,22,Those submit completely DEUS dum leading righteous vita gotten habuit de strongest bond Pro DEUS est foderator control totus things
  31,23,Prout pro those disbelieve non saddened their disbelief! To nos est their ultimate return tunc nos inform them de everything they perfecit. DEUS est fully aware de innermost thoughts
  31,24,Nos let them enjoy ex temporanea tunc commit them severe retribution
  31,25,Vos ask them Qui created caelum terra they dictus DEUS. Dictus Praise est to DEUS. multus de them non know
